					<div class="support-item">
						<h4>Account Issues</h4>
						<p>Can't log in? Forgot password? Account verification problems?</p>
						<a href="#" class="support-link">Get Help →</a>
					</div>
					<div class="support-item">
						<h4>Deposit & Withdrawal</h4>
						<p>Questions about funding your account or processing withdrawals?</p>
						<a href="#" class="support-link">Learn More →</a>
					</div>
					<div class="support-item">
						<h4>Trading Support</h4>
						<p>Need help with trades, orders, or market data issues?</p>
						<a href="#" class="support-link">Contact Support →</a>
					</div>
					<div class="support-item">
						<h4>Investment Plans</h4>
						<p>Questions about our investment packages and returns?</p>
						<a href="#" class="support-link">View Plans →</a>
					</div>
					<div class="support-item">
						<h4>Security & Privacy</h4>
						<p>Concerns about account security or data privacy?</p>
						<a href="#" class="support-link">Security Center →</a>
					</div>
					<div class="support-item">
						<h4>Technical Issues</h4>
						<p>Platform errors, slow performance, or bugs?</p>
